---
title: Curried Chickpea Burgers with Tomato, Tangy Mayo & Roasted Broccoli
description: We LOVE a burger, and we know you do too! Luckily our chefs know how to keep the romance alive. These swoony chickpea burgers are packed with fragrant curry powder, scallions, and dill. They’re pan-fried until crisp on the outside and tender on the inside, then tucked onto buttery toasted buns, slathered with tangy apricot-Dijon mayo and juicy tomato slices. This charmer comes with roasted potato wedges on the side because we heart you.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66c6243f5cb721784e63849e-258c0a74.jpeg
